HR NO. 195 ENROLLED
THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED that the House of Representatives of the
Legislature of Louisiana does hereby designate Monday, April 27, 2026, as Louisiana Young
Heroes Day at the state capitol and does hereby commend the Louisiana Public Broadcasting
2026 Louisiana Young Heroes for their outstanding contributions to the state and its citizens.
